<br>
After my mailbox was spammed with requests to remove her from the board and/or lock the topics this post came up, I asked Noonie to very reasonably let this discussion drop and end.  This was taking the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  same general topic</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> that was locked in the general forum -- Mages vs. Wizards and Mage Balance issues -- and letting it surface once again here with a violent twist.  Apparently she thought because &quot;anything goes&quot; here she could bring this topic back up w/o the possibility of it being &quot;censored&quot; or locked and, at the same time, start a massive flame war in this forum.  <br>
<br>
There is a line that must be drawn everywhere, even if anything goes.  This thread belongs in neither the general forum (because of the excessive written violence) or the rant forum (because it contains class discussion). <br>
<br>
Ask your self a simple question, had I have not of taken action where/when would this thread have ended?  I think you'll find yourself at the same conclusion I came to.  I even asked anyone who felt I treated Noonie unfairly to email me... none did.<br>
<br>
Edit: Just to clear it up, she wasn't banned for having her own ideas, she was banned because of the increasingly violent nature she was taking on (evident in other posts on this board) and a few other reasons.  She wasn't banned because she couldn't argue her points heh.. if that was the case I would have to ban myself sometimes. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A> at: 12/31/01 7:40:41 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaurianne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aurianne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 9:19:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: my rant.</span><hr size=1> Hmm.... no more bullshit from Noonie in a while... been blocked?<br>
