Now.... 1+1 != 2<br>
<br>
a = b <br>
a^2 = b^2<br>
a^2 - b^2 = 0<br>
(a+b)(a-b) = 0<br>
a+b = 0<br>
2a = 0<br>
2 = 0<br>
<br>
<br>
And we know that 1+1 is not equal to zero.... /grin<br>
